      <h3>Motivation</h3>
      <p>I wanted a quick way to find colors within a gradient as usually those colors work well together overall in a palette. With those colors I can create more art (which mainly currently consists of making <a href="https://giphy.com/channel/gyhwa" target="_blank">GIPHY gifs</a>)!</p>
    </div>
