  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <h3>Website</h3>
      <p>This website is built off of tinygradient to generate the gradients and uses color-convert to quickly get the HEX, CMYK, and HSV from the tineygradient.</p>
      <p>The website uses Node.js and EJS in combination with Bootstrap to make it run.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
