    <div class="col">
      <h3>Future Steps</h3>
      <p>Other features I want to explore in the future is to make it so that you can easily get an .ase file of all the swatches. Another potential solution is to do something similar to <a href="https://coolors.co/" target="_blank">coolors</a> or <a href="https://colorhunt.co/" target="_blank">Color Hunt</a> where you can export an image.</p>
